|\sum _{ k=1 }^{ n }{ z_{ k } } |=\sum _{ k=1 }^{ n }{ |z_{ k }| } \Longleftrightarrow \arg(z_1)=\arg(z_2)=\cdots=\arg(z_n) 
z_k=r_k e^{i\phi}
\sum_k z_k=e^{i\phi}\sum_k r_k
